<bibRefCitation author="Fage" box="[1165,1286,224,248]" pageId="6" pageNumber="487" refString="Fage, L. (1942) Mysidacea Lophogastrida. II. The Carlsberg Foundation's oceanographical expedition round the world 1928 - 1930 and previous &quot; Dana &quot; expeditions under the leadership of Prof. Johannes Schmidt. Dana Report, 4 (23) 1 - 67." type="journal article" year="1942">Fage 1942</bibRefCitation>
